com.github.robtimus.junit.support.extension.testlogger

Class JdkLoggerContext

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.github.robtimus.junit.support.extension.testlogger.JdkLoggerContext

  • public final class JdkLoggerContext
extends Object
    JdkLoggerContext represents a JDK Logger. It can be injected using TestLogger, TestLogger.ForClass or TestLogger.Root, and can be used to configure the logger for test purposes.
    Author:
    Rob Spoor
    Since:
    2.1
